quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,11,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vakauya nemanyepo (vachipomera Aishah (RA) mukadzi wamutumwa Muhammad (SAW)) iboka riri pakati penyu. Musafunge kuti zvakakuipirai, asi zvakakunakirai. Munhu wese pakati pavo ane zvaachawana kubva kuchivi. Uye uyo pakati pavo akaita chidimbu chikuru (mumanyepo Abdullah ibn Ubayy), achawana mutongo mukuru (marwadzo makuru)"
  24,12,"Sei, pamakazvinzwa, vatendi varume nevakadzi vasina kufunga zvakanaka pamusoro pavo pachavo (pakati pavo), uye vakati: “Aya ndiwo manyepo ari pachena?”"
  24,13,"Sei avo (vakanyepa) vasina kuuya nevapupuri vana (4)? Uye nokuti havana kuuya nevapupuri, zvino ndivo mumeso aAllah vanyepi"
  24,14,"Uye dai dzisiri nyasha dzaAllah kwamuri uye tsitsi dzavo munyika uye muhupenyu hwekudenga (mushure mekufa), maizobatwa nemarwadzo makuru nekuda kweizvo zvamakataura (manyepo)"
  24,15,"Makazvitambira (nekuzviparadzira) nerurimi rwenyu, uye mukazvitaura nemiromo yenyu izvo zvamange musina ruzivo nazvo, uye mukafunga kuti hazvina basa (hazvina kukosha), izvo zviri mumeso aAllah zvikuru"
  24,16,"Uye sei pamakazvinzwa musina kutaura kuti: “Hazvina kukodzera kwatiri kutaura nezvazvo. Mukuru ndimi (Allah)! Aya manyepo makuru.”"
  24,17,"Allah vanokuyambirai kuti musadzokera kune zvakafanana naizvo zvachose, kana muri vatendi"
  24,18,"Uye Allah vanokujekeserai mitemo (humboo, zviratidzo), uye Allah vanoziva zvese, uye vane ungwaru hwese"
  24,19,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanoda (chivi che) hupombwe chive chinoteurwa pakati peavo vanotenda, vachave nemarwadzo makuru munyika muno uye muhupenyu hwekudenga (mushure mekufa). Uye Allah vanoziva, asi imi (vanhu) hamuzivi"
  24,20,"Uye dai dzisiri nyasha dzaAllah kwamuri (vanhu) uye tsitsi dzavo (Allah vaikurangai nekukurumidza). Uye nokuti Allah vane ngoni zhinji, uye tsitsi dzakawanda"